    source = os.path.join(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)), 'app', 'ui', 'resources.qrc')
    target = os.path.join(os.path.dirname(os.path.abspath(__file__)), 'app', 'resources_rc.py')

    os.popen(cmd)
